  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h1>About BurnLink</h1>
        <p class="intro">BurnLink is a zero-knowledge file sharing service. Files are encrypted in your browser before they leave your device. We store only the encrypted payload and have no ability to read your data.</p>

        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <ul class="plain-list">
          <li>Your file is encrypted in-browser using AES-256-GCM before upload</li>
          <li>The server stores only the encrypted payload, never unencrypted data</li>
          <li>Sharing links are invalidated after the first download</li>
          <li>Optional password protection with 10-minute lockout after 3 failed attempts</li>
          <li>Zero-knowledge architecture — we cannot access your files</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Privacy first</strong>
            <p>Your files are encrypted in your browser. We never see the unencrypted content.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>One-time access</strong>
            <p>Files are deleted immediately after the first download.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Optional passwords</strong>
            <p>Add password protection for an extra layer of security.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Open source</strong>
            <p>Transparent code, transparent choices. Auditable by anyone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Why BurnLink?</h2>
        <ul class="plain-list">
          <li>Traditional cloud storage keeps files indefinitely</li>
          <li>Email attachments are exposed through message systems</li>
          <li>Most sharing services can read your data</li>
          <li>BurnLink gives you control and privacy</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Share a file</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost">View on GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

